<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٣٨ ... سُورَةُ ص ... آياتها ٨٨ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِي الذِّكْرِ}</span> ... المُشْتَمِلِ عَلَى تَذْكِيرِ النَّاسِ بِمَا هُمْ عَنْهُ غَافِلُونَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عِزَّةٍ}</span> ... تَكَبُّرٍ، وَحَمِيَّةٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشِقَاقٍ}</span> ... مُخَالَفَةٍ، وَعِنَادٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَمْ أَهْلَكْنَا}</span> ... كَثِيرًا مِنَ الأُمَمِ أَهْلَكْنَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَرْنٍ}</span> ... أُمَّةٍ سَابِقَةٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَاتَ حِينَ مَنَاصٍ}</span> ... لَيْسَ الوَقْتُ وَقْتَ فِرَارٍ وَخَلَاصٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عُجَابٌ}</span> ... عَجِيبٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَلَأُ}</span> ... الأَشْرَافُ، وَكِبَارُ القَوْمِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{امْشُوا}</span> ... اسْتَمِرُّوا عَلَى دِينِكُمْ، وَشِرْكِكُمْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَشَيْءٌ يُرَادُ}</span> ... مُدَبَّرٌ يُقْصَدُ مِنْهُ التَّرَؤُسُ، وَالسِّيَادَةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمِلَّةِ الْآخِرَةِ}</span> ... دِينِ آبَائِنَا وَدِينِ النَّصَارَى.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اخْتِلَاقٌ}</span> ... كَذِبٌ، وَافْتِرَاءٌ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلْيَرْتَقُوا فِي الْأَسْبَابِ}</span> ... فَلْيَاخُذُوا بِالأَسْبَابِ المُوصِلَةِ إِلَى السَّمَاءِ، وَلْيَمْنُعوا الوَحْيَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جُندٌ مَّا}</span> ... جُنُودٌ قَلِيلُونَ حَقِيرُونَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذُو الْأَوْتَادِ}</span> ... صَاحِبُ الجُنُودِ، وَالقُوَّةِ العَظِيمَةِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>